                           <name type="place" key="HjaMos02">ytra Hiarda<supplied reason="unknown">r</supplied>dal</name>
                           i nundar firde, konu <name type="person" key="JonSte005">Jons Steindorsſonar
                                 yngra</name>. Eru med hendi Steindors
                              ormsſonar. <name type="person" key="ArnMag001">A. M.</name></q>
