                        </item>
                     <item>På <locus from="accMat02r" to="accMat02v">seddel b</locus> 
                        (<dimensions type="slip" unit="mm"><height unit="mm">160</height><width unit="mm">140</width></dimensions>) har
                        <name key="ArnMag001" type="person">Arne Magnusson</name> skrevet: 
                        <q>Halldor Biarnaſon i Breidadal i Onundarfirde
